# ====================================================================
# Atlantic Quest — fichero de partida nueva
# Pantalla 512x512 (mapa) + 100px panel derecho
# SCALE=20, grid 25x25 celdas (cada celda 20x20 px)
# Posiciones: en pixeles, multiplos de SCALE para encajar en celda exacta.
# ====================================================================


# ====================================================================
# SPACES (10)
# Cada space tiene su PNG en ./img_src/background/<filename>
# Layout del juego: 3 caminos paralelos desde el Loby hasta los bosses
#
#                        +---------+
#                        |  Loby   | (1)
#                        +---------+
#                       /     |     \
#                      W      S      E
#                      |      |      |
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#                | Cor_l | | Cor_c | | Cor_r |  (4) (6) (2)
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#                    |        |        |
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#                | End_l | | Cor_e | | End_r |  (5) (7) (3)
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#                    |        |        |
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#                |Boss_l | |Boss_e | |Boss_r |  (9) (10) (8)
#                +-------+ +-------+ +-------+
#
# Formato: id|name|gdesc(path_to_png)|OST|line0|line1|...|line24
# Cada line es WIDHT (=25) caracteres: '1'=transitable, '0'=pared
# ====================================================================
